sentences.english: DNP treatment reduced the alternative respiration pathway capacity.
sentences.chinese: 而DNP處理則降低交替呼吸途徑容量。

sentences.english: The centralization and the decentralization in the old China competed and alternate mutually.
sentences.chinese: 舊中國中央集權與地方分權相互競爭，相互交替。

sentences.english: At this point you must alternate lateral and radial truing . Be patient.
sentences.chinese: 在這點上你必須交替的從側面和縱向進行調整。
走好運與倒黴交替發生。

sentences.english: It showed that the ratio of alternative pathway in total respiration increased during fruit browned.
sentences.chinese: 果實褐變時，果成交替途徑呼吸比例增高。

sentences.english: Alternating between a deterministic and a non-deterministic node selection effectively solves the bottleneck problem.
sentences.chinese: 確定與非確定性節點選擇交替有效地解決了瓶頸問題。

sentences.english: Why can my hand be when is season alternant desquamate?
sentences.chinese: 我的手爲什麼會在季節交替的時候脫皮呢？

sentences.english: The girl comes to her employer's house to work on alternate days.
sentences.chinese: 這個女孩交替地去她的僱主家幹活。

sentences.english: Alternating direction methods are suitable ones for solving large-scale problems.
sentences.chinese: 交替方向法適合於求解大規模問題。

sentences.english: Alternating and moving my feet one inch at a time.
sentences.chinese: 兩條腿交替向前挪步，一次挪一英寸。

sentences.english: So do the dual forces of the Tao wax and wane in the alternation of upward and downward cycles, intercrossing.
sentences.chinese: 在升降的交替中，道的盛衰盈虧兩個力量也是如此。
世代交替的甜蜜，是否遭背叛？

sentences.english: Linear structure forms localized bond in strong-weak cycles.
sentences.chinese: 線形結構大多形成強弱交替的定域鍵。

sentences.english: An ordinary meter will not respond to these rapid alterations .
sentences.chinese: 普通的電流計無法響應這些快速的交替變化。

sentences.english: The experimental results show that transfer of interior moisture mainly controls the drying process.
sentences.chinese: 並採用冷熱風交替的乾燥方法將取得較好的節能效果。

sentences.english: This paper presents a new alternating direction method for a class of variational inequalities.
sentences.chinese: 該文對於一類變分不等式提出了一種新的交替方向法。
